 \frac{d}{du} u=1= 2x \frac{\partial x}{\partial u} -2y \frac{\partial y}{\partial u} \\ \frac{d}{du} v=0= 2x \frac{\partial x}{\partial u} -\frac{\partial y}{\partial u} 
 \left(\begin{array}{cc}2x&-2y\\2x&-1\end{array}\right)\left(\begin{array}{c}x_u\\ y_u\end{array}\right)=\left(\begin{array}{c}1\\ 0\end{array}\right) 
